    "description": "《星际尼莫》是一款建造平台益智游戏，旨在为你提供最有趣的外太空体验。<br><br>在广袤的星系疆域中采矿期间，四位Hypergiant Inc.员工迫降在一颗小行星上，并被绝望地困在了那里。<br><br>为了使他们能够与自己的船队重聚，你必须帮助他们走遍这颗星球表面的每一寸土地、以独特而创造性的方式解开谜题，然后建造一艘飞船并为它加满燃料，从而重返太空。<br><br>凭借离奇的系列任务和拓展想象力边界的自定义工具，《星际尼莫》将平台玩法和自定义升华到了星际境界乃至更高。<br><br><br><strong>开拓一整个星系</strong><br>一项充满乐趣的系列任务，以图瑞里亚和阿卡拉行星为背景，外加三颗迷你卫星以及数不清的发现，更有其他行星与卫星将会陆续推出。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/d0082e92d0f388b28082f593e4986a0a.poster.avif?t=1756928433\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/d0082e92d0f388b28082f593e4986a0a.webm?t=1756928433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/d0082e92d0f388b28082f593e4986a0a.mp4?t=1756928433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>与好友共享无限乐趣</strong><br>与多达三位其他本地或线上玩家合作，想方设法通过利用古怪的构件、发现秘密和探索行星，实现携手重返家园的目标。<br><br>随遇而安。欣赏音乐。在太空中释放自我。《星际尼莫》的唯一主题就是享受快乐并与新朋老友分享回忆。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/a3cd39fa623069b98eed10e82883b373.poster.avif?t=1756928433\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/a3cd39fa623069b98eed10e82883b373.webm?t=1756928433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/a3cd39fa623069b98eed10e82883b373.mp4?t=1756928433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>勾勒宇宙</strong><br>世界编辑器提供了精细的工具，供你建造和填充自己的行星，实现无与伦比的细节水平，并通过Steam创意工坊分享你的杰作。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/eb6cf8edd02d54ac8e11bc47ca99fec8.poster.avif?t=1756928433\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/eb6cf8edd02d54ac8e11bc47ca99fec8.webm?t=1756928433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/eb6cf8edd02d54ac8e11bc47ca99fec8.mp4?t=1756928433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>拖、放并分发</strong><br>创意工坊令创造简单到难以置信。只要你能想到，那么借助《星际尼莫》，你就能造出来！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/54558a230e9b53a4544d44e8612e0858.poster.avif?t=1756928433\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/54558a230e9b53a4544d44e8612e0858.webm?t=1756928433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/54558a230e9b53a4544d44e8612e0858.mp4?t=1756928433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
